<li id="cite_note-2"><b><a href="#cite_ref-2" title="">^</a></b> <a href="/wiki/Walter_Laqueur" title="Walter Laqueur">Walter Laqueur</a> (2006): <i>The Changing Face of Anti-Semitism: From Ancient Times to the Present Day</i>, Oxford University Press, p.41 <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0195304292" class="internal">ISBN 0-19-530429-2</a></li>
