<li id="cite_note-10"><b><a href="#cite_ref-10" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="book" id="CITEREF.5B.5BNorman_Davies.5D.5D1996"><a href="/wiki/Norman_Davies" title="Norman Davies">Norman Davies</a> (1996). <i><a href="/wiki/Europe:_A_History" title="Europe: A History">Europe: A History</a></i>. pp.&#160;412. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0198201710" class="internal">ISBN 0-19-820171-0</a>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=%5B%5BEurope%3A+A+History%5D%5D&amp;rft.aulast=%5B%5BNorman+Davies%5D%5D&amp;rft.au=%5B%5BNorman+Davies%5D%5D&amp;rft.date=1996&amp;rft.pages=pp.%26nbsp%3B412&amp;rft.isbn=0-19-820171-0&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Pogrom"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
