<li id="cite_note-12"><b><a href="#cite_ref-12" title="">^</a></b> <a href="/wiki/Robert_Michael" title="Robert Michael">Michael, Robert</a>. "Luther, Luther Scholars, and the Jews," <i>Encounter</i> 46:4, (1985)</li>
